acceptance_criteria: runCli keeps its synchronous signature with zero spec-file edits; full suite passes; local test-mode wall time reduced by at least 3x from the 17+min baseline; spawn semantics preserved for cwd/input call sites and via PM_TEST_CLI_RUNNER=spawn escape hatch
risk: medium
confidence: high
resolution: fixed
expected_result: runCli keeps its synchronous signature with zero spec-file edits; full suite passes; local test-mode wall time reduced by at least 3x from the 17+min baseline
actual_result: "Sync worker bridge shipped (Atomics.wait + receiveMessageOnPort, single dist import per worker, taint-based reuse across test contexts with route-independent extension/schema taint detection, spawn fallback for cwd/stdin/timeout/worker-death). Full suite 5563/5563 green in 4m19s vitest wall (baseline 17-25+min, worst files 330s->~30s; help-runtime 250s->15s). One iteration of per-test disposal measured 9m45s before taint-based reuse landed 4m19s."
